'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #3022] on 20 November 2000 at 11:58:10 am'!"Change Set:		FullBoundsFixDate:			20 November 2000Author:			Dan IngallsReestablishes the layout paradigm in TransformMorph, which had overridden fullBounds with no propagation of ownerChanged."!!TransformMorph methodsFor: 'geometry' stamp: 'di 11/20/2000 11:54'!fullBounds	"Overridden to clip submorph hit detection to my bounds."	"It might be better to override doLayoutIn:, and remove this method"	fullBounds ifNotNil:[^ fullBounds].	fullBounds _ bounds.	submorphs do: [:m| m ownerChanged].	^ fullBounds! !